  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO CREATE THE \"MARKET-READY HOMES REVOLVING LOAN PROGRAM\" TO ASSIST HOMEOWNERS WITH MAKING NECESSARY REPAIRS AND UPGRADES TO EXISTING HOMES TO ESTABLISH AN ENHANCED POST-REPAIR LISTING PRICE WITH LENDING OPTIONS FOR THE HOMEOWNER; TO CREATE THE \"MARKET-READY HOMES REVOLVING LOAN FUND\" IN THE STATE TREASURY; TO PROVIDE THAT THE PROGRAM AND FUND SHALL BE ADMINISTERED BY THE MISSISSIPPI HOME CORPORATION; TO PROVIDE ELIGIBILITY AND CONDITIONS FOR MAKING LOANS FROM THE FUND; TO AMEND SECTION 43-33-717, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO CONFORM; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
  },
